Company Overview of Chevron Lubricants Lanka PLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Chevron Lubricants Lanka PLC engages in blending, manufacturing, importing, distributing, and marketing lubricant oils, greases, brake fluids, and specialty products in Sri Lanka. The company offers passenger vehicle, four stroke motor cycle, two stroke and outboard, diesel vehicle, and marine engine oils; and general purpose automotive gear oils, automatic transmission oils, industrial lubricants, coolants, and other products under the Havoline, Delo, and Caltex brands. It also provides in-service oil monitoring, systematic failure analysis expertise, seminar, plant and lab visit, lubrication survey, drain interval optimization, product bulletin/guide/other publication, and endoscope inspec...
Chevron Lubricants Lanka PLC engages in blending, manufacturing, importing, distributing, and marketing lubricant oils, greases, brake fluids, and specialty products in Sri Lanka. The company offers passenger vehicle, four stroke motor cycle, two stroke and outboard, diesel vehicle, and marine engine oils; and general purpose automotive gear oils, automatic transmission oils, industrial lubricants, coolants, and other products under the Havoline, Delo, and Caltex brands. It also provides in-service oil monitoring, systematic failure analysis expertise, seminar, plant and lab visit, lubrication survey, drain interval optimization, product bulletin/guide/other publication, and endoscope inspection services, as well as health, environment, and safety support services; and lube specialist courses, channel partner workshops, remote thermo meters, vehicle clinics, and portable test kits. The company also exports its products to Bangladesh and Maldives. The company was incorporated in 1992 and is based in Colombo, Sri Lanka. Chevron Lubricants Lanka PLC is a subsidiary of Chevron Ceylon Limited.
Detailed Description


