Product List | Welcome to Chevron Lubricant Lanka PLC.























































 » Product List


Product List







For almost three-quarters of a century, Chevron has been manufacturing and marketing quality lubricants around the world. In today’s highly complex and competitive market, Chevron’s high performance brands and value-added services are a result of the combination of resources and technology of the entire Chevron Lubricants organization. Well-known brands such as Havoline, Delo and Caltex have established both a local and international reputation for reliability and unsurpassed quality and performance. Among the company’s comprehensive range of products, the Lanka branded items which were formally a local product but subsequently brought under the Caltex umbrella maintaining international standards, have held a firm reputation for excellence and performance in Sri Lanka.
Our brands stand for quality, value and service. Most importantly, it stands for our commitment to you-our customer. Our creed of quality, professionalism, service and efficiency dictates that you are always satisfied with our distinctive value offer and exceptional product portfolio.
 










