Company Description                    




                        Chevron Lubricants Lanka PLC engages in blending, manufacturing, importing, distributing, and marketing lubricant oils, greases, break fluids, and specialty products in Sri Lanka. The company offers its products for industrial, commercial, and consumer applications. Chevron Lubricants Lanka PLC markets its products under Chevron, Caltex, and Texaco brands. The company was incorporated in 1992 and is based in Colombo, Sri Lanka.                    


